description:
An Electron-based application to generate WAV files synchronised with GPS time from the files generated by the AudioMoth-GPS-Sync firmware.

**Please Note**: This is an automatically updated package. If you find it is out of date by more than a day or two, please contact the maintainer(s) and let them know the package is no longer updating correctly.
summary: An Electron-based application to generate WAV files synchronised with GPS time from the files generated by the AudioMoth-GPS-Sync firmware.
